name: Large Design
description: Large tattoo design is anything from a chest-piece to sleeve designs, provided they're possible to design! If confused as to which category your idea falls under, just contact me via email at: Hannahkatephotog@ymail.com Before checkout, email me the specifications of your design and I'll get to work straight off.

name: Medium Design
description: Medium tattoo design a design which involves more than one component, but isn't anything as large as a back-piece/chest-piece. Half-sleeves fall in this category. Anything larger will fall under other categories. If confused as to which category your idea falls under, just contact me via email at: Hannahkatephotog@ymail.com Before checkout, email me the specifications of your design and I'll get to work straight off.

name: Small design
description: Small tattoo design is anything simplistic which is composed of one component, such as the rose at the header of this page. Anything larger will fall under other categories. If confused as to which category your idea falls under, just contact me via email at: Hannahkatephotog@ymail.com Before checkout, email me the specifications of your design and I'll get to work straight off.
